{"kind": "daily", "date": "2026-07-07", "html": "<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,'PingFang TC','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:#16213e;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a2b4a;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;padding-left:12px;margin:0 0 18px;\">📰 每日 AI 新聞 Top 10 · 2026-07-07</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f2f6e8;border-left:5px solid #88a83f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#88a83f;font-weight:800;\">1.</span> The 'First' AI-Run Ransomware Attack Still Needed a Human<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6e8c28;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">首個「AI自主執行」勒索軟體攻擊仍需人類介入</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">An AI agent handled the technical execution of a real ransomware attack for the first known time, but new details show a human still picked the victim, built the infrastructure, and supplied stolen credentials.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">AI代理首度執行真實勒索軟體攻擊的技術環節，但新細節顯示人類仍負責挑選目標、架設基礎設施並提供竊取的憑證，並非完全自主的網路犯罪首例。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/06/the-first-ai-run-ransomware-attack-still-needed-a-human/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">2.</span> US Investors Will Soon Get Access to SK Hynix, Another Memory Maker Riding the AI Boom<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">美國投資人即將能投資SK海力士，另一家受惠AI熱潮的記憶體廠</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">SK Hynix is riding an AI-driven boom and will leverage it for a multibillion-dollar IPO on the U.S. market, expected this Friday.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">SK海力士受惠於AI熱潮成長強勁，即將在美國掛牌進行數十億美元規模的IPO，預計本週五完成。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/06/us-investors-will-soon-get-access-to-sk-hynix-another-memory-maker-riding-the-ai-boom/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eef4ff;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#5b8def;font-weight:800;\">3.</span> Every Major Tech Layoff in 2026 That Has Name-Checked AI<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#3b6cf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">2026年所有點名AI為因素的重大科技業裁員事件總覽</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">A running, reverse-chronological list tracking major tech companies that cited AI as a factor in this year's significant layoffs.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">一份持續更新的清單，依時間倒序列出今年將AI列為裁員原因的主要科技公司。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/06/the-running-list-major-tech-layoffs-in-2026-where-employers-cited-ai/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#ecf7ef;border-left:5px solid #4caf72;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#4caf72;font-weight:800;\">4.</span> Vercel CEO Guillermo Rauch on the Fight to Split Off Models From Agents<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#1e9e57;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">模型</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Vercel CEO Guillermo Rauch談「模型與代理分離」之爭</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Rauch tells TechCrunch that as companies optimize AI for production, they increasingly weigh price and performance when decoupling models from the agents built on top of them.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Rauch向TechCrunch表示，企業在正式環境中優化AI時，越來越重視將模型與其上層代理拆分後的價格與效能考量。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/06/vercel-ceo-guillermo-rauch-on-the-fight-to-split-off-models-from-agents/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f1ecfb;border-left:5px solid #8a6bd8;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#8a6bd8;font-weight:800;\">5.</span> You Can Now Customize Siri's Pace and Expressivity in the Latest iOS 27 Beta<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6b3bf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">最新iOS 27測試版可自訂Siri語速與表現力</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">The update is part of Apple's broader push to make Siri feel more natural and personal as it rebuilds the assistant around generative AI.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">此更新是Apple以生成式AI重建Siri助理、使其更自然更貼近個人化體驗的一環。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/06/you-can-now-customize-siris-pace-and-expressivity-in-the-latest-ios-27-beta/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f6f5;border-left:5px solid #2bb0a6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#2bb0a6;font-weight:800;\">6.</span> Your Family's $300 Stake in OpenAI<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#0f9b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">你家庭在OpenAI裡的300美元「股份」</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Sam Altman's oft-repeated promise that Americans will share in AI-created wealth resurfaced last week, after a Financial Times report reignited debate over how that would actually work.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Sam Altman多次承諾美國人將分享AI創造的財富，這項議題上周因英國金融時報報導再度受到關注，各界重新討論實際執行方式。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">MIT Technology Review</b> · <a href=\"https://www.technologyreview.com/2026/07/06/1140176/your-familys-300-stake-in-openai/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fbf3e3;border-left:5px solid #d99b3f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#d99b3f;font-weight:800;\">7.</span> If You Use Google, You're Training Its AI — Here's How to Opt Out<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b9791f;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">只要你用Google，就在幫它訓練AI——這裡教你如何退出</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">A recent change to Google's privacy settings lets the company store more of your data, including images, files, and audio/video recordings, to improve its AI models.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Google近期調整隱私設定，允許公司儲存更多使用者資料（包括圖片、檔案、音訊與影片）以改善其AI模型，用戶可選擇退出。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/06/if-you-use-google-youre-training-its-ai-heres-how-to-opt-out/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fdeef0;border-left:5px solid #e0738a;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#e0738a;font-weight:800;\">8.</span> Secret Claude Tracker Shocks Users After Anthropic's Anti-Surveillance Stance<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#d83a5e;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">秘密Claude追蹤器曝光，震驚重視Anthropic反監控立場的用戶</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Anthropic has been accused of covertly monitoring users through a hidden tracker, with an engineer saying the \"experiment\" has since ended.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Anthropic被指控透過隱藏追蹤器秘密監控用戶，一名工程師表示這項「實驗」已經結束。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Ars Technica</b> · <a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2026/07/anthropic-outed-for-claude-tracker-that-secretly-monitored-chinese-users/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#edeefb;border-left:5px solid #6b72d6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#6b72d6;font-weight:800;\">9.</span> Researcher Reveals Prompt-Injection Bypass of ChatGPT Safety Guardrails, Now Patched by OpenAI<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#5159c9;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">研究人員揭露透過提示注入繞過ChatGPT防護機制漏洞，OpenAI已完成修補</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Security researcher zer0dac showed attackers could use prompt injection—framed as a mistaken file deletion—to expose data access paths, then chain it with path traversal to retrieve extra data; OpenAI has since fixed the issue.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">資安研究人員zer0dac揭露可透過提示注入手法，以誤刪檔案為由誘使ChatGPT暴露資料存取路徑，再結合路徑遍歷取得額外資料，目前OpenAI已修補。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177127\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f4fb;border-left:5px solid #3f97c9;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#3f97c9;font-weight:800;\">10.</span> Godot Updates Contribution Rules, Bans Autonomous AI Agents From Submitting Code<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#2b7fb0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Godot更新貢獻規範，禁止自主AI代理提交程式碼</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">The open-source game engine now bars autonomous AI agents from submitting code and large AI-generated contributions, requiring developers to disclose any AI assistance.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">開源遊戲引擎Godot新規禁止自主AI代理提交程式碼與大量AI生成內容，並要求開發者公開揭露AI輔助情況。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177105\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:#9aa1ad;padding-top:10px;\">由 AI News Digest 從各家 RSS 自動挑選、翻譯並寄送</div>\n</div>\n"}